Structure.Name: Unused
Structure.Comment: Always sent as -1 in the Flash client. This is most likely leftover from the transition to the Flash client. Teleporters worked differently in the Shockwave client where entering a room trough teleports used a special packet GOVIADOOR which carried over the teleported id.
Client calls this 'State', unused since the introduction of wardrobe. Maybe related to whatever to auto open the side menu?
